{"id":538402,"date":[{"year":1974,"month":8,"day":28}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"红小兵批林批孔儿歌选,把中小学的批林批孔运动抓紧抓好","genre":"","count":"142","ytitle":"","mtitle":"今日咱批《神童诗》","ftitle":"","authors":["王锋"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑞金南路小学六(2)班　王锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《神童诗》，害人诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“神童”是个大骗子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“读书做官”放毒气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“天才史观”臭东西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通篇宣扬坏思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字里行间有毒汁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日咱批《神童诗》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马列主义作武器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深挖“神童”老根子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命到底志不移!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\08\\748s031301.JPG\">"}]}